The Afro Mermaid 🧜🏽‍♀️ 

The new Little Mermaid is so important because black and brown boys and girls are able to feel seen and represented in a major way. 

Thank you to @hallebailey and @disney @disneylittlemermaid for this masterpiece. Celebrating differences and being inclusive should be normalized whether it’s a movie, cartoon, etc. Everyone deserves to feel seen.
